{"id":12189,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/12189","type":2,"name":"鬼神伝","name_cn":"鬼神传","summary":"生活在京都的天童纯是个不太有自信的十五岁男孩。父亲七年之前死于事故，此后纯一直和母亲两个人过日子。这天，纯在放学回家的路上被神秘魔物追赶，危急之中逃入一所古寺，僧人源云救了他。谁知纯就此被带往时空的彼方……\r\n恢复意识的纯发现自己竟身处平安时代的京都。纯从贵族那里听说了关于“鬼”的事情。“鬼”使用各种妖术操控自然、危害人们的生活。而穿越时空而来的纯正是能唤醒幻之大蛇、结束纷争的“拯救之神子”。了解到自己的身份之后，纯感到不知所措。\r\n鬼族少女水叶告诉纯，“鬼”并不是恶魔，而是力图与自然共存的人。哪一方说的是真话？我又该守护哪一方？在纯的踌躇矛盾之中，人与鬼的大决战临近了……","eps":[{"id":859494,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/859494","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"eps_count":1,"air_date":"2011-04-29","air_weekday":5,"rating":{"total":111,"count":{"1":1,"2":3,"3":9,"4":17,"5":21,"6":40,"7":14,"8":3,"9":2,"10":1},"score":5.4},"rank":5852,"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/ab/2b/12189_7c0H3.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/ab/2b/12189_7c0H3.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ab/2b/12189_7c0H3.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/ab/2b/12189_7c0H3.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/ab/2b/12189_7c0H3.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":144,"collect":161,"doing":3,"on_hold":10,"dropped":13},"crt":null,"staff":[{"id":15485,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/15485","name":"高田崇史","name_cn":"","role_name":"","images":null,"comment":1,"collects":0,"info":{"alias":{"kana":"たかだ たかふみ"},"birth":"1958年12月"},"jobs":["原作"]},{"id":2089,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/2089","name":"川崎博嗣","name_cn":"川崎博嗣","role_name":"","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/bf/42/2089_prsn_anidb.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/bf/42/2089_prsn_anidb.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/bf/42/2089_prsn_anidb.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/bf/42/2089_prsn_anidb.jpg"},"comment":3,"collects":0,"info":{"name_cn":"川崎博嗣","alias":{"kana":"かわさきひろつぐ","romaji":"Kawasaki Hirotsugu"},"gender":"男","birth":"1958年12月7日"},"jobs":["导演","脚本"]},{"id":74,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/74","name":"荒川稔久","name_cn":"荒川稔久","role_name":"","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/